sentences: Jeff Hughell (born December 4, 1979) is the former bassist for Asylum, Vile and Brain Drill and the current bassist for Six Feet Under and Reciprocal.
Hughell is currently endorsed by Warwick bass guitars, Seymour Duncan pickups and Dean Markley strings.
